'''''Out of the Shadows''''' is an [[action-adventure game]] developed for the [[ZX Spectrum]] by R.M. Waller and R.M.R. Woodward.<ref name="wos">{{cite web|url=http://www.worldofspectrum.org/infoseekid.cgi?id=0006772|title=Out of the Shadows|work=World of Spectrum|accessdate=2008-12-08}}</ref> It was published in 1984 by Mizar Computing and in 1986 on the compilation ''Fourmost Adventures'' by Global Software.<ref name="wos"/>

