''Out of the Shadows'' received a "Crash Smash" from ''[[CRASH (magazine)|CRASH]]'' magazine, who highlighted the novel light and shadow concept and overall complexity of the gameplay.<ref name="crash">{{cite journal |journal=CRASH |url=http://www.crashonline.org.uk/11/outofts.htm |issue=11 |date=December 1984 |title=CRASH 11 - Out of the Shadows}}</ref>

